<title>train and test</title>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing text_cell rendered"><div class="prompt input_prompt">
</div><div class="inner_cell">
<div class="text_cell_render border-box-sizing rendered_html">
<p><b>Problem:- You will be predicting the costs of used cars given the data collected from various sources and distributed across various locations in India.</b><br>
FEATURES:<br>
Name: The brand and model of the car.</p>
<p>Location: The location in which the car is being sold or is available for purchase.</p>
<p>Year: The year or edition of the model.</p>
<p>Kilometers_Driven: The total kilometres driven in the car by the previous owner(s) in KM.</p>
<p>Fuel_Type: The type of fuel used by the car.</p>
<p>Transmission: The type of transmission used by the car.</p>
<p>Owner_Type: Whether the ownership is Firsthand, Second hand or other.</p>
<p>Mileage: The standard mileage offered by the car company in kmpl or km/kg</p>
<p>Engine: The displacement volume of the engine in cc.</p>
<p>Power: The maximum power of the engine in bhp.</p>
<p>Seats: The number of seats in the car.</p>
<p>New_Price: The price of a new car of the same model.</p>
<p>Price: The price of the used car in INR Lakhs.</p>

</div>
</div>
</div>

<p><h1>REMOVING OUTLIERS:&lt;/H1&gt;</p>

</div>

</div>
<div class="cell border-box-sizing code_cell rendered">
<div class="input">

<div class="inner_cell">
    <div class="input_area">
<div class=" highlight hl-ipython3"><pre><span></span><span class="n">Q1</span> <span class="o">=</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">quantile</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.25</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">Q3</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">quantile</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mf">0.75</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">IQR</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">Q3</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="n">Q1</span>
<span class="nb">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">IQR</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="n">train</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="p">[((</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span><span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Kilometers_Driven</span><span class="p">)))]</span>
<span class="n">train</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="p">[((</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span><span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Mileage</span><span class="p">)))]</span>
<span class="n">train</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="p">[((</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span><span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Engine</span><span class="p">)))]</span>
<span class="n">train</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="p">[((</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Power</span><span class="p">)))]</span>
<span class="n">train</span><span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">train</span><span class="p">[((</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span> <span class="o">&gt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q1</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span> <span class="o">-</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span><span class="p">))</span> <span class="o">&amp;</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">train</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span> <span class="o">&lt;=</span> <span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Q3</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mf">1.5</span> <span class="o">*</span> <span class="n">IQR</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">Price</span><span class="p">)))]</span>
<span class="n">train</span>
</pre></div>

    <span class="n">scores</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">model_selection</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">cross_val_score</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">model</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">X_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">y_test</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">cv</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">k_folds</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">scoring</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s1">&#39;r2&#39;</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">Avg_Score</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="n">np</span><span class="o">.</span><span class="n">mean</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">scores</span><span class="p">)</span>  
    <span class="k">return</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">Avg_Score</span><span class="p">)</span>
